(3593, 5, 'story_0_story_header', 'Chances are, you imagined someone in an exam room with a runny nose, a broken arm, or an itchy rash.\r\n'),
(3594, 5, '_story_0_story_header', 'field_56b838619ca3d'),
(3595, 5, 'story_0_story_text', 'Sure, that’s a part of it. But we’re patients well before we put on a paper gown – when we’re checking insurance benefits, finding a doctor, submitting claims, filling prescriptions… We need someone to look after us then, too.\r\n'),
(3596, 5, '_story_0_story_text', 'field_56b838e7923b2'),
(3597, 5, 'story_1_story_header', 'Zocdoc is for patients.\r\n'),
(3598, 5, '_story_1_story_header', 'field_56b838619ca3d'),
(3599, 5, 'story_1_story_text', 'We created Zocdoc to solve patient problems, beginning with online appointment-booking – and we haven’t stopped building since. With Zocdoc, you can see doctors’ open appointment times and book instantly online, make informed choices with verified reviews, and stay on top of important checkups with tailored reminders. And those pesky waiting room forms? Fill them out online, just once, and keep them forever.'),
(3600, 5, '_story_1_story_text', 'field_56b838e7923b2'),
(3601, 5, 'story_2_story_header', 'We’ll keep dreaming up solutions. '),
(3602, 5, '_story_2_story_header', 'field_56b838619ca3d'),
(3603, 5, 'story_2_story_text', 'Of course, your healthcare experience probably isn’t perfect yet. But no matter what, we’ll continue to put the patient’s needs first. We simply believe there’s no better way to deliver the great healthcare experience we all deserve.\r\n'),
