(172, 2, '2016-01-19 15:50:05', '2016-01-19 15:50:05', 'Jeff Bezos has always been interested in anything that can be revolutionized by computers. Intrigued by the amazing growth in use of the Internet, Jeff created a business model that leveraged the Internet''s unique ability to deliver huge amounts of information rapidly and efficiently. In 1994 he founded Amazon.', 'Bezos Expeditions', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bezos-expeditions', '', '', '2016-01-31 21:13:57', '2016-01-31 21:13:57', '', 0, 'http://zocdocstatic.wpengine.com/?post_type=investors&#038;p=172', 1, 'investors', '', 0),
(173, 2, '2016-01-19 15:50:26', '2016-01-19 15:50:26', 'Marc Benioff is Chairman and CEO of Salesforce.com. He founded the company in 1999 with a vision to create an on-demand information management service that would replace traditional enterprise software technology. Benioff is regarded as the leader of what he has termed "The End of Software," the now proven belief that multi-tenant, cloud computing applications democratize information by delivering immediate benefits at reduced risks and costs.', 'Marc Benioff', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'marc-benioff', '', '', '2016-01-31 21:14:08', '2016-01-31 21:14:08', '', 0, 'http://zocdocstatic.wpengine.com/?post_type=investors&#038;p=173', 2, 'investors', '', 0),
(174, 2, '2016-01-19 15:50:49', '2016-01-19 15:50:49', 'The Founders Fund provides capital to transformational businesses run by world-class entrepreneurs; companies the firm has backed include Facebook, Quantcast, SpaceX, Palantir Technologies, RoboteX, and ZocDoc. The firm, which pursues a founder-friendly investment strategy, is managed by four partners, all of whom are themselves company founders: Peter Thiel (PayPal; Palantir); Ken Howery (PayPal); Luke Nosek (PayPal); and Sean Parker (Napster; Plaxo; founding president, Facebook). Founders Fund is represented on the ZocDoc board by Ken Howery.', 'Founders Fund', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'founders-fund', '', '', '2016-01-31 21:14:18', '2016-01-31 21:14:18', '', 0, 'http://zocdocstatic.wpengine.com/?post_type=investors&#038;p=174', 3, 'investors', '', 0),
