(475, 2, '2016-01-21 15:30:37', '2016-01-21 15:30:37', 'Our service was built so you don’t have to book appointments over the phone! We''re working hard to create a simple online healthcare experience – but if you''re having trouble, give us a call at (855) 962-3621 and we''ll be happy to guide you through the booking process.', 'Can I call ZocDoc to book my appointments over the phone?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '432-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-01-21 15:30:37', '2016-01-21 15:30:37', '', 432, 'http://zocdocstatic.wpengine.com/432-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
